---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Terms of Use" description="FieldHealth Africa terms of use — rules governing use of this website and its tools.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">

    <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl text-white mb-4">Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <!-- Non-clinical disclaimer — must be prominent -->
    <div class="rounded-xl bg-amber-500/[0.07] border border-amber-500/25 p-5 text-sm text-amber-200/80 leading-relaxed mb-10">
      <p class="font-semibold text-amber-300 mb-2">⚠ Important — Not for clinical use</p>
      <p>The tools provided by FieldHealth Africa are designed exclusively for <strong class="text-amber-200">administrative, operational, and educational purposes</strong> in health-system management. They are not intended to support, replace, or influence individual clinical decisions, diagnoses, or treatment plans. Always consult a qualified healthcare professional for clinical matters. Use of any tool on this site for clinical decision-making is at the user's sole risk.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-10 text-white/65 text-sm leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">1. Acceptance of terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing or using fieldhealthafrica.org (the "Site"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Use. If you do not agree, please do not use the Site. These terms apply to all visitors, registered users, and anyone who accesses or uses the Site in any way.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
